{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":31,"text":"This is really a two-hour presentation\nI give to high school students,"},{"time":3345,"text":"cut down to three minutes."},{"time":4620,"text":"And it all started one day\non a plane, on my way to TED,"},{"time":7285,"text":"seven years ago."},{"time":8603,"text":"And in the seat next to me\nwas a high school student, a teenager,"},{"time":13000,"text":"and she came from a really poor family."},{"time":15483,"text":"And she wanted to make\nsomething of her life,"},{"time":18000,"text":"and she asked me a simple little question."},{"time":20063,"text":"She said, \"What leads to success?\""},{"time":22032,"text":"And I felt really badly,"},{"time":23435,"text":"because I couldn't give her a good answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25920,"text":"So I get off the plane, and I come to TED."},{"time":28000,"text":"And I think, jeez, I'm in the middle\nof a room of successful people!"},{"time":31754,"text":"So why don't I ask them\nwhat helped them succeed,"},{"time":34389,"text":"and pass it on to kids?"},{"time":36817,"text":"So here we are, seven years,\n500 interviews later,"},{"time":40450,"text":"and I'm going to tell you\nwhat really leads to success"},{"time":43414,"text":"and makes TEDsters tick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45367,"text":"And the first thing is passion."},{"time":47787,"text":"Freeman Thomas says,\n\"I'm driven by my passion.\""},{"time":50763,"text":"TEDsters do it for love;\nthey don't do it for money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53247,"text":"Carol Coletta says, \"I would pay\nsomeone to do what I do.\""},{"time":56755,"text":"And the interesting thing is:"},{"time":58190,"text":"if you do it for love,\nthe money comes anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60866,"text":"Work! Rupert Murdoch said\nto me, \"It's all hard work."},{"time":64000,"text":"Nothing comes easily.\nBut I have a lot of fun.\""},{"time":67107,"text":"Did he say fun? Rupert? Yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":70001,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71501,"text":"TEDsters do have fun working.\nAnd they work hard."},{"time":74271,"text":"I figured, they're not workaholics.\nThey're workafrolics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77248,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78862,"text":"Good!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":79943,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80968,"text":"Alex Garden says, \"To be successful,\nput your nose down in something"},{"time":84338,"text":"and get damn good at it.\""},{"time":85608,"text":"There's no magic;\nit's practice, practice, practice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88474,"text":"And it's focus."},{"time":89517,"text":"Norman Jewison said to me,"},{"time":91275,"text":"\"I think it all has to do\nwith focusing yourself on one thing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":94773,"text":"And push!"},{"time":96235,"text":"David Gallo says, \"Push yourself."},{"time":98247,"text":"Physically, mentally,\nyou've got to push, push, push.\""},{"time":100913,"text":"You've got to push through shyness\nand self-doubt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103548,"text":"Goldie Hawn says,\n\"I always had self-doubts."},{"time":106000,"text":"I wasn't good enough;\nI wasn't smart enough."},{"time":108120,"text":"I didn't think I'd make it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":110264,"text":"Now it's not always easy to push yourself,"},{"time":112327,"text":"and that's why they invented mothers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114439,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115439,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":117000,"text":"Frank Gehry said to me,"},{"time":120000,"text":"\"My mother pushed me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":121394,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122632,"text":"Serve!"},{"time":124427,"text":"Sherwin Nuland says,\n\"It was a privilege to serve as a doctor.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":128093,"text":"A lot of kids want to be millionaires."},{"time":130227,"text":"The first thing I say is:"},{"time":131501,"text":"\"OK, well you can't serve yourself;"},{"time":133427,"text":"you've got to serve others\nsomething of value."},{"time":135688,"text":"Because that's the way\npeople really get rich.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":139074,"text":"Ideas!"},{"time":140123,"text":"TEDster Bill Gates says, \"I had an idea:"},{"time":143000,"text":"founding the first micro-computer\nsoftware company.\""},{"time":146000,"text":"I'd say it was a pretty good idea."},{"time":148000,"text":"And there's no magic to creativity\nin coming up with ideas --"},{"time":151000,"text":"it's just doing some very simple things."},{"time":153359,"text":"And I give lots of evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155291,"text":"Persist!"},{"time":156799,"text":"Joe Kraus says,"},{"time":157824,"text":"\"Persistence is the number\none reason for our success.\""},{"time":160832,"text":"You've got to persist through failure.\nYou've got to persist through crap!"},{"time":164398,"text":"Which of course means \"Criticism,\nRejection, Assholes and Pressure.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":167937,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170727,"text":"So, the answer to this question is simple:"},{"time":174470,"text":"Pay 4,000 bucks and come to TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176619,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177836,"text":"Or failing that, do\nthe eight things -- and trust me,"},{"time":180598,"text":"these are the big eight things\nthat lead to success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183842,"text":"Thank you TEDsters\nfor all your interviews!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186585,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}